      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776682047623,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In case one of the APIs will error out, error msg will be\ndisplayed. And the user can try again, in case of\nsuccess, the team will be generated.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In case one of the APIs will error out, error msg will be displayed. And the user can try again, in case of success, the team will be generated.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sqFbwmWefBWXagOp4N7RT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1693.8518876806338,
      "y": 34.10740192500543,
      "width": 728.0590209960938,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6d",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 217870194,
      "version": 115,
      "versionNonce": 753596978,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776682047623,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Initially the player will set the lineup by selecting the\nposition on the field component, after generate will\nbe enabled",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Initially the player will set the lineup by selecting the position on the field component, after generate will be enabled",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "eca6mmJkKHWHOb-u7ahIz",
